{"word":"ματάω","slug":"ματάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n65234\" key=\"mata/w\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">μᾰτάω</orth>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">μάτην</etym>):—poet. Verb, <sense id=\"n65234.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">to be idle, dally</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἀπέκοψε παρήορον οὐδὲ μάτησε</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:16:474\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">16.474</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:23:510\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">23.510</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μὴ τὼ μὲν</foreign> (sc. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἵππω</foreign>)<cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">δείσαντε ματήσετον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:233\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.233</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οὐ ματᾷ τοὔργον</foreign> the work <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">lags</tr_> not, goes on apace, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg003.perseus-grc1:57\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pr.\">Pr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">57</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ματᾶν ὁδῷ</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">to loiter</tr_> by the way, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg004.perseus-grc1:37\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\